sequenceDiagram
    participant FE as 前端 SPA
    participant H as admin.Handler
    participant M as models (provider_usage)
    participant DB as SQLite

    FE->>H: GET /admin/api/provider-usage
    H->>H: ListProviders() → []ProviderRecord

    loop 每个 provider
        H->>M: CurrentCycleWindow(p.CycleStartDate)
        M-->>H: (cycleStart, cycleEnd)
    end

    par 并行：消耗聚合
        H->>M: AggregateProviderUsage(DB, cycleStart)
        M->>DB: SELECT SUM(tokens), SUM(calls) FROM call_logs WHERE DATE(created_at) >= ?
        DB-->>M: map[slug]*ProviderMonthlyUsage
    and 并行：分配聚合（逐个 provider）
        loop 每个 provider
            H->>M: GetProviderAllocation(DB, slug)
            M->>DB: SELECT SUM(token_limit WHERE >0), SUM(call_limit WHERE >0), COUNT(token=0) FROM users JOIN quotas WHERE fixed_provider=? AND active
            DB-->>M: *ProviderAllocation
        end
    end

    loop 每个 provider
        H->>M: BuildProviderUsageView(p, usage[p.Slug], allocation, globalTokenRatio, globalCallRatio)
        Note over M: 消耗低余额 = IsLowBalance(used, limit, ratio)
        Note over M: 分配超额   = IsLowBalance(allocated, limit, ratio)
        Note over M: 周期剩余天数 = end - today
        M-->>H: ProviderUsageView (完整含 allocation + cycle)
    end

    H-->>FE: {data: []ProviderUsageView}
    Note over FE: 列表 4 列：Token消耗 | Token分配 | Call消耗 | Call分配
    Note over FE: 仪表盘 4 行 + 周期起止 + 剩余天数
    Note over FE: 分配超额标红（仅提醒不拦截）
